.content-main-header
  %h1.f300 Advisory Council

.panel{ style: 'margin-bottom: 30px' }
  .panel-body
    %p.lead
      The Sleep Apnea Patient Centered Outcomes Network (SAPCON) Advisory Council brings together a range of professionals and researchers to help us develop our platform. Each member has been active in the field of sleep research and treatment.

- @pc["members"].each do |member|
  .panel.advisory-small{ data: { toggle: 'collapse', target: "#collapse#{member['name'].gsub(/\s+/, '')}" } }
    %h5
      = member["name"]
      - if member["title"]
        %span= member["title"]
    %h6= member["loc"]
    %p.collapse{ id: "collapse#{member['name'].gsub(/\s+/, '')}"}= member["bio"]
